496
00:36:46,239 --> 00:36:50,619
"'Apakah Sang Penghukum Seorang Kriminal?'"

497
00:36:55,119 --> 00:36:56,450
"'Akankah Kwon Soo Chul Dibebaskan Lagi setelah Delapan Tahun?'"

498
00:36:56,890 --> 00:36:58,059
"Apa Keringanan Hukum usai Berdamai dengan Korban Hal Yang Adil?""

499
00:37:47,609 --> 00:37:48,710
Lihat itu.

500
00:37:49,640 --> 00:37:50,739
Ada apa?

501
00:37:52,679 --> 00:37:54,549
Kwon Soo Chul masih dipenjara.

502
00:37:54,549 --> 00:37:56,379
Dia menculik orang lain?

503
00:37:56,379 --> 00:37:57,580
Lagi?

504
00:38:07,729 --> 00:38:09,929
Aku yakin banyak dari kalian yang penasaran denganku.

505
00:38:10,600 --> 00:38:12,229
Namaku Kang Woo Joon.

506
00:38:14,270 --> 00:38:15,799
Foto yang kalian lihat barusan...

507
00:38:21,439 --> 00:38:23,439
Dia istriku, Lee Yoo Jung.

508
00:38:26,439 --> 00:38:28,479
Yoo Jung meninggal delapan tahun silam.

509
00:38:31,080 --> 00:38:32,580
Ini Kwon Soo Chul.

510
00:38:33,049 --> 00:38:34,220
Dialah pria

511
