00:45:31,340 --> 00:45:33,940
- Tangkap dia!
- Hentikan mereka!

630
00:45:33,940 --> 00:45:35,609
- Hentikan dia!
- Tangkap dia!

631
00:45:35,609 --> 00:45:38,139
- Cegah mereka pergi!
- Hentikan dia!

632
00:45:47,090 --> 00:45:48,889
Kamu yakin aku dilindungi dengan sepantasnya?

633
00:45:49,119 --> 00:45:50,190
Kenapa?

634
00:45:50,519 --> 00:45:52,389
Kamu takut? Takut?

635
00:46:09,470 --> 00:46:10,540
"Real Estat Bintang"

636
00:46:10,710 --> 00:46:13,080
Kami akan menemuimiu di belakang gedung.

637
00:46:13,080 --> 00:46:14,409
- Lewat sini.
- Baik, Pak.

638
00:46:14,850 --> 00:46:17,180
Perhatian, Para Penghuni.

639
00:46:17,550 --> 00:46:19,050
Kami sedang bekerja sama

640
00:46:19,050 --> 00:46:21,790
- dengan kepolisian saat ini.
- Pakai tangga!

641
00:46:22,450 --> 00:46:25,519
Tolong bekerja sama dengan opsir polisi.

642
00:46:25,519 --> 00:46:26,519
Bau.

643
00:46:27,359 --> 00:46:28,960
