- Tidak ada.

644
00:46:28,960 --> 00:46:30,060
Di luar.

645
00:46:30,060 --> 00:46:32,029
Mari bertemu di titik temu lantai satu.

646
00:46:32,029 --> 00:46:34,269
- Kami akan keluar dahulu. Baik.
- Ya, Pak.

647
00:46:51,220 --> 00:46:52,279
"Polisi"

648
00:47:23,680 --> 00:47:24,779
Kamu!

649
00:47:34,729 --> 00:47:35,729
Bedebah.

650
00:47:42,629 --> 00:47:43,800
Kamu tidak apa-apa?

651
