00:48:31,919 --> 00:48:33,219
Tidak!

654
00:48:36,919 --> 00:48:38,060
Kang Woo Joon!

655
00:48:42,929 --> 00:48:43,929
Kumohon

656
00:48:44,300 --> 00:48:45,359
Jangan!

657
00:48:50,469 --> 00:48:52,270
Sial. Kamu.

658
00:48:57,169 --> 00:48:59,780
Jangan, ampuni aku.

659
00:49:03,919 --> 00:49:04,980
- Tidak.
- Kang Woo Joon!

660
00:49:04,980 --> 00:49:06,879
Tolong ampuni aku.

661
00:49:12,260 --> 00:49:13,290
Kang Woo Joon.

662
00:49:14,260 --> 00:49:15,760
Sudah lihat hasil pemungutan suaranya?

663
00:49:17,399 --> 00:49:19,899
Orang-orang memutuskan membiarkan Kwon Soo Chul hidup.

664
00:49:23,969 --> 00:49:27,969
"Bunuh, 47 persen, Ampuni, 51 persen"

665
00:49:29,340 --> 00:49:30,939
Katamu kamu mau melakukan hal yang benar.

666
00:49:31,179 --> 00:49:32,679
Kamu mau orang-orang

667
